{"tid":442100,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"等你地食m記食得咁開心","createTime":"2017-10-20T09:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T11:25:43.000Z","uid":34730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"694e1fb2faacd3d8d709aa9b475e26220ec33732","tid":442100,"uid":34730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T09:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日去食m記<br />\n斜對面枱有對父女<br />\n個女就好曳既<br />\n成餐又大叫又爬枱<br />\n個呀爸點鬧都搞佢唔掂<br />\n跟住食食下個女無啦啦企係到屙尿<br />\n之後個呀爸話個女屙尿做乜唔話佢知<br />\n之後急急腳抱個女走左<br />\n然後m記清潔婆婆就行過黎拎條毛巾抹左d尿<br />\n但個婆婆就唔知係尿黎<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後抹完地下個婆婆將d尿就咁扭落垃圾桶<br />\n條毛巾就繼續拎去抹餐盆同枱....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/20/175159_5048b0082ad0ef89e4fb004fd2d35efb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F20%2F175159_5048b0082ad0ef89e4fb004fd2d35efb.jpg&h=41a47f31&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5039ef04a7e5c8220cd8bbf0fbcb66374c17ca4","tid":442100,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T09:54:13.000Z","msg":"麥樂雞都係咁食啦"},{"pid":"3a8707c103efda6208c123bee6e7cc7636732a3c","tid":442100,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T09:54:32.000Z","msg":"出得街食嘢預左 咩餐廳都好"},{"pid":"81e2b5cf1113a839c8db6f8a8a871a9975415af1","tid":442100,"uid":34730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T10:04:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出得街食嘢預左 咩餐廳都好</blockquote><br />\n預左都唔好做得咁光明正大"},{"pid":"880d34a185349c321e12fe8af663813a5dec8104","tid":442100,"uid":127075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T10:04:47.000Z","msg":"冇人叫你堂食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5293df56ec7134f7c81e862546594d85da9a39c","tid":442100,"uid":2137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T10:07:20.000Z","msg":"童子尿好嘢來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e19393f42406ae557cb0f961cd9892583a85ca1b","tid":442100,"uid":107656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T10:16:15.000Z","msg":"係處女既尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106f3e71e3dbe4746492b74b8a1c7b79572e3a84","tid":442100,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T10:17:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係處女既尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f83a09b645739dbf8b5e873e1e287c24e395b7","tid":442100,"uid":34730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:25:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇人叫你堂食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n堂食都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}